      "content": "Yes, you must finish the entire 10-day course even if the redness is gone, because stopping early can leave surviving bacteria that become resistant to future treatments. Completing the full dose ensures the infection is completely eradicated and prevents the need for stronger medications later. Taking antibiotics only when necessary is good for your health, but once prescribed, the full duration is critical for your safety.",
