      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but it feels like a lot of unnecessary medicine for no reason if the skin is already healthy. if i just stop now, what actually happens? like, is it really going to make a difference if the visible symptoms are 100% gone? i'd rather just let my immune system handle the rest than keep flooding my body with drugs.",
